@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Communicate

actor UserA
actor UserB
participant "ControllerInput Manager" as CIM
participant "HUD" as HUD
participant "CollaborationCommunication Manager" as CCM
participant "VoiceChatManager" as VoiceChat
participant "Network Manager" as NM
participant "Event Logger" as EL

== Proximity Voice Chat (Vivox Positional Audio) ==
UserA -> VoiceChat: Connect to Vivox channel (on spawn)
VoiceChat -> NM: Set3DAudio(headTransform)
NM -> VoiceChat: Positional audio active

UserA -> NM: Moves closer to UserB
NM -> VoiceChat: UpdateVoicePosition(headOrigin)
VoiceChat -> VoiceChat: Adjust volume based on 3D distance
UserA -> CIM: Speaks (voice input)
CIM -> VoiceChat: Capture audio
VoiceChat -> NM: Broadcast positional voice to UserB
NM -> UserB: Deliver voice (distance-attenuated)

alt UserA leaves UserB's range
    UserA -> NM: Moves away from UserB
    NM -> VoiceChat: UpdateVoicePosition(headOrigin)
    VoiceChat -> VoiceChat: Volume decreases with distance
    CCM -> EL: Log proximity/volume event
    EL -> EL: Log Mute Action
end

== Self-Mute ==
UserA -> CIM: Toggle mute
CIM -> VoiceChat: ToggleSelfMute(true/false)
VoiceChat -> NM: selfMuted.Value = true/false (NetworkVariable)
NM -> UserB: Sync mute state (all clients)

== Public ChatBox Flow (Text) ==
UserA -> HUD: Opens HUD
HUD -> CCM: Selects public chat
CCM -> NM: Get message history
NM --> CCM: Returns messages
CCM -> HUD: Shows history
UserA -> CIM: Types message, clicks send
CIM -> CCM: Forwards message
CCM -> NM: Broadcasts to all users in room
CCM -> EL: Log message event
EL -> EL: Log Message

== Private ChatBox Flow (Text) ==
UserA -> HUD: Selects UserB for private chat
UserA -> CIM: Points at UserB, selects chat option
CIM -> CCM: Initiate private chat
CCM -> NM: Opens private chat channel
NM -> UserB: Deliver private message

note over VoiceChat, NM
    Vivox positional audio (XRINetworkPlayer.SetVoiceId)
    drives 3D attenuation via VivoxParticipant.
    selfMuted is a NetworkVariable synced to all clients.
end note
@enduml
